  "prompt": "What is the best free online course for website design?",
  "response": "There are several excellent free online courses for website design that cater to different skill levels and aspects of web development. Here are some of the top recommendations:\n\n1. **Coursera - Web Design for Everybody: Basics of Web Development & Coding Specialization**: Offered by the University of Michigan, this specialization covers HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The first course is free to audit, and it provides a comprehensive introduction to web design.\n\n2. **edX - Introduction to HTML and CSS**: Provided by the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C), this course offers foundational knowledge in HTML and CSS, which are essential for website design.\n\n3. **FreeCodeCamp**: This is a popular platform that offers a comprehensive, self-paced curriculum on web design and development. It covers responsive web design, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, all through hands-on projects.\n\n4. **Udacity - Intro to HTML and CSS**: This is a free course that teaches the basics of HTML and CSS, ideal for beginners. It\u2019s a part of Udacity\u2019s broader offerings and includes interactive exercises.\n\n5. **Codecademy - Learn HTML & CSS**: Codecademy offers a free, interactive platform where you can learn HTML and CSS. The basic courses are free, with the option to subscribe for more advanced topics.\n\n6. **Khan Academy - Intro to JS: Drawing & Animation**: While primarily focused on JavaScript, this course helps build website interactivity and can be beneficial for those interested in adding animations and graphics to their web designs.\n\n7. **Google\u2019s Web Fundamentals**: This resource offers a wealth of information on modern web design practices and technologies, including performance, user experience, and how to create responsive designs.\n\n8. **YouTube Tutorials**: There are numerous YouTube channels like \"Traversy Media,\" \"The Net Ninja,\" and others that offer free tutorials on web design, covering various aspects from basic to advanced topics.\n\nThese courses and resources provide a solid foundation for anyone looking to start learning about website design.",
